latestPosts.caption:
the bridal shower of my dreams!!! 💐🎀💍 

#bridalshower #bride #bridetobe #2026bride #bridalshowerideas

Feeling so showered with love from this weekend 💐🎀

There’s something really special about walking into a room full of women you love — and who love you right back. It’s emotional in a way I wasn’t expecting.

Planning a shower in Jersey while living in Florida wasn’t the easiest, but it came together thanks to so many incredible women — especially to my rockstar of a mom who truly went above and beyond to make my shower unforgettable.

Thank you to everyone who showed up, sent love, or helped bring this day to life. Wedding era is officially in motion!! 🥹💍

#bridalshower #bridetobe #2026bride
